<h2>Chapter 2: The 5 Essential Email Automation Workflows &#123;#ch2&#125;</h2>
<p>Every home service business needs five core automation workflows. These are not optional extras. They are the infrastructure that captures revenue you are currently losing.</p>
<h3>Workflow 1: Estimate Follow-Up Sequence</h3>
<p>This is the highest-revenue workflow. Most businesses send one follow-up email, if any. The best-performing sequences send 4 to 6 emails over 7 to 14 days.</p>
